As far as pulling yah, sure our new lull is fine, you can use it to keep froming getting adds... why is the agro range remaining the same?  People say &quot;so we can't lull our way through content&quot;.  Yah thats cute cause last I remember spells could be partially effective... thanks SoE for cutting another corner, coulda just made some monster immune to the agro reduction (don't know the exact term for that but where with our old lull you could lull walk up to it slap its face and it would still stand there.  Now you lull with the new one, break a twig 2 miles away and it still comes for you).
<br />

<br />
I think I agree alot with the original poster in the general idea of what is happening to bards, my theory? Dev's are lazy. don't want to fix things the right way but rather cut a corner.  Could also be SoE management saying &quot;you have x time do it if you want your paycheck&quot; so the dev's are forced to do things the easier ways because of work load, I can't say for sure.
