<br />

<br />
I didn't play bard in FFXI because I thought they were not only the complete form of &quot;mana b!tchs&quot; (yes not all mana but full group support I know but its the same for this example), but that I really thought EQ had done a beautiful job of creating a bard class, no other game has done even close to as good as EQ in my opinion, but now it seems EQ wants to simulate other games rather than be unique.
